These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, water-polo, cycling
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
3. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Sport   | cycling | water-polo | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, gardening, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | dancing | rock-climbing | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, sprite
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | coffee | sprite |

 #################################

 
